.******************************************************************************
.* System         : ALL                                                       *
.*                                                                            *
.* Include Name   : DXPATDOC.PBL                                              *
.*                                                                            *
.* Function       : To Display a description from the PATDO1FD file           *
.*                                                                            *
.* Author         : Justin Coates      11/02/1992                             *
.*                                                                            *
.* Parameters     : CCOL & CVERT  display positions                           *
.*                  KEY6          doctor code                                 *
.*                                                                            *
.* Modifications  :                                                           *
.*        V5.10.B01  17/04/2001  Tonii  SRF 647825                            *
.*                   Opened PATDO1A1 to avooid I * C error                    *
.******************************************************************************
DXPATDOC  PACK      PACFNAME,SP30,SP30,SP30      * clear name
          MATCH     SP6,KEY6                     * is there a code
          IF        !@EQUAL
            MOVE      "Invalid Doctor Code",PACFNAME
            OPEN      PATDO1A1,"patdo1af"
            CALL      RDDOCT1
            IF        OVRCD <> 1
              MOVE      DSNAME,PACSNAME
              MOVE      DGNAME,PACGNAME
              MOVE      DTITL,PACTITLE
              MOVE      TWO,PACFRMT
              CALL      PACNAME
            ENDIF
          ENDIF
          PACK      VAR,PACFNAME,SP30,SP30,SP30
          CALL      DISPITEM                * display variable
          RETURN
